            "title": "A股半日跌  滬股曾升6點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日收跌，滬股一度倒升，深股則曾跌近1%，兩市成交合計15850.57億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指半日報4139點，跌7點或0.17%，今早開見4128，跌18點或0.43%，為半日低，其後跌幅收窄，最高見4152，升6點或0.14%，為半日高位，半日成交6742.79億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日報14405點，跌98點或0.68%，最低見14366，跌137點或0.94%，跌幅其後收窄，最高見14472，跌31點或0.21%，為半日高位，半日成交9107.78億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300半日跌33點或0.71%，報4693點 ; 創業板指數跌48點或1.48%，報3296點。</p>\n</div>",
