            "title": "港股開升66點   藥業股升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數開升66點或0.25%，報26447，恒生科技指數升7點或0.15%，報5117 ; 國指開升3點或0.04%，報8817點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交27.43億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230823_FI_source-web_02269-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230823_FI_source-web_02269-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藥明生物(02269)升4.86%，報40.14元，虧轉盈的百濟神州(06160)跌0.72%，報193元。再鼎醫藥(09688)升4.9%，報15.19元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)升1.24%，報146.8元 ; 友邦(01299)升1.24%報85.75元 ; 中國平安(02318)升1.11%，報68.6元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">商湯(00020)升4.1%，報2.54元。</p>\n</div>",
